Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它将几乎由\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It would consist almost entirely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一种叫中子的亚原子粒子组成\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of subatomic particles called neutrons,
