Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自从兹威基预测这个现象存在后的35年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And 35 years after Zwicky predicted their existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:18.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天文学家开始找到它们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}astronomers began to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们将它们称为"脉冲星"\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We call them "pulsars"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:24.35,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们在快速自转的同时会发射出有规律的脉冲电波信号\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when they spin rapidly and emit regular pulses of radio energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超新星与中子星都能发出\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Supernovas and neutron stars could account
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大量的宇宙射线\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for a wide range of cosmic rays,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但不是能量最强的那种\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but not the most energetic ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在的科学还不能很好解释这种现象\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nothing yet known to science
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:36.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过没事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can explain them, and we're fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我爱科学的原因之一\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's one of the things I love about science,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们从不假装自己知道所有的答案\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we don't have to pretend we have all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.77,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兹威基还认为\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Zwicky also came up with the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}星系的重力会让它四周的空间结构发生弯曲\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the gravity of a galaxy warps the fabric
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:48.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像放大镜一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of space around it, to act like a lens.
