Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:57.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它与我们过去以为很了解的那个宇宙一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And just like the one we thought we knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}充满了奥秘\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it was filled with mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.91,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暗物质完全是探测不到的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Dark matter is completely unobservable,
